==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nobody
<hw>No"bod*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Nobodies</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[<ets>No</ets>, a. +
<ets>body</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>No person; no one; not
anybody.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Hence:</specif> <def>A person of no influence or
importance; an insignificant or contemptible person.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nocake</ent>⟦br⟧
